{"tid":1054484,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨遊盡量live]屋久島種子島backpack行～","createTime":"2019-03-09T22:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T13:17:53.000Z","uid":236845,"like":6,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b85b9a50f3a728d0e7b2eac648a64eda2a79bad4","tid":1054484,"uid":236845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:36:22.000Z","msg":"第一次係LIGHK出油雞(之前都係其他forum出)，多多指教～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自從幾年前睇左秒速5厘米後，一直都想去一次種子島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但一直都只係得個&ldquo;講&rdquo;字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身為一個Y4學生，眼見距離進入社會大學既日子好快就到，假期足亦會越來越少，所以上個月決定把握機會來再一場&ldquo;說走就走的出走&rdquo;，去一個我一直好想去既地方&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;種子島&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講，直接簡略講吓今次行程。<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: HKG&gt;KOJ &gt; 通宵船去屋久島<br />\nDay 2: 屋久島行山 (宿屋久島)<br />\nDay 3: 屋久島&gt;種子島 (宿種子島)<br />\nDay 4: 種子島 (宿種子島)<br />\nDay 5: 種子島&gt;鹿兒島 (宿鹿兒島)<br />\nDay 6: KOJ&gt;HKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後比個溫馨提示先，我一向奉行&ldquo;花少錢，去多次&rdquo;原則，所以我今次都係廉遊為主，如果你係鍾意豪華遊又睇唔起其他人廉遊嘅話，你依家可以按上一頁出返去先啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁依家正式開始LIVE啦！(戴返個頭盔先，係&ldquo;盡量Live&quot;咋!!)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次坐UO546 7:55起飛，所以要坐5：50第一班機鐵出發，順便係香港站攞埋boarding pass～～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrhMQec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrhMQec.jpg&h=7d1b3de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6：20到機場，去M記食個早餐先～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwJHozn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwJHozn.jpg&h=6283c230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7hXWUo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7hXWUo.jpg&h=404177ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4aVJz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4aVJz2.jpg&h=599a3a87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a1990b714c4c2976f36c8afe6599176cfe523b6","tid":1054484,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:44:39.000Z","msg":"今日飛？"},{"pid":"7812ffd3eebd3c15438291956fed697a50257706","tid":1054484,"uid":236845,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a1990b714c4c2976f36c8afe6599176cfe523b6","tid":1054484,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:44:39.000Z","msg":"今日飛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:49:28.000Z","msg":"話明Live緊係今日飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，啱啱食完早餐"},{"pid":"77a57347e327f7818e640bdf06c0087bcccf08aa","tid":1054484,"uid":136952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7812ffd3eebd3c15438291956fed697a50257706","tid":1054484,"uid":236845,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a1990b714c4c2976f36c8afe6599176cfe523b6","tid":1054484,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:44:39.000Z","msg":"今日飛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:49:28.000Z","msg":"話明Live緊係今日飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，啱啱食完早餐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:50:34.000Z","msg":"730機？"},{"pid":"8cffb827341ede3b1a3dfb5a350bc2c29b4e5b0d","tid":1054484,"uid":236845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"77a57347e327f7818e640bdf06c0087bcccf08aa","tid":1054484,"uid":136952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7812ffd3eebd3c15438291956fed697a50257706","tid":1054484,"uid":236845,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a1990b714c4c2976f36c8afe6599176cfe523b6","tid":1054484,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T22:44:39.000Z","msg":